Anyone who knows me knows I LOVE music. As an instructor at
@flywheelsports, I listen to music for hours trying to find the perfect songs to curate playlists that will get my students motivated to work harder. Thank you, @iamplusofficial & @iamwill, for gifting me these dope new wireless headphones! Now I can listen to music anywhere feeling the vibes and getting inspired in everything I do. 🎶
GUYS, check out my bio link! I made you a RAD playlist w/ 20 of my favorite tunes.
